00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,700
別這樣
No.

456
00:33:23,330 --> 00:33:24,370
請不要傷害我

457
00:33:24,710 --> 00:33:27,770
好的 沒事的 放輕鬆
Okay. It's okay, it's okay, it's okay.

458
00:33:27,770 --> 00:33:31,540
我、我不太明白你在說什麼 但
Please. I-I don't understand what you're saying, but...

459
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:33,480
聽著 請冷靜下來
Listen. Please calm down.

460
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:35,650
