你說過
You said.

469
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:22,400
他們將參與革命
They'll be revolutionaries.

470
00:34:28,370 --> 00:34:30,670
七個小時了 還沒有消息
Seven hours now, no news.

471
00:34:31,770 --> 00:34:33,840
這次有點奇怪
This time, it's different.

472
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:36,740
他們都在工作中 伊扎克
They are doing what they are doing, Yitzhak.

473
00:34:36,740 --> 00:34:39,480
你現在什麼也做不了
There is nothing you can do about it.

474
