00:41:52,010 --> 00:41:54,850
聽到你自己名字的時候 站起來
When you hear your name, you stand up,

552
00:41:54,850 --> 00:41:58,890
到這兒拿著你的護照到另一個房間去
come collect your passport and go to the other room.

553
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:03,220
阿爾瑪格 艾澤拉
Almog, Ezra.

554
00:42:06,530 --> 00:42:08,990
科恩 帕斯科
Cohen, Pasco.

555
00:42:08,990 --> 00:42:10,530
來吧 來吧
Come on, come on.

556
00:42:10,530 --> 00:42:12,530
快 快 快 過來
Fast, fast, fast. Come here.

557
00:42:12,530 --> 00:42:14,530
斯坦伯格 馬克
Steinberg, Mark.

558
00:42:18,470 --> 00:42:19,440
艾布拉姆斯 伊薩克
Abrams, Isaac

559
00:42:19,740 --> 00:42:20,660
我們沒同意過這個

560
00:42:20,780 --> 00:42:23,080
-放鬆點
-都是放屁 他們在騙我們

561
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:23,370
魯本斯 邁克爾
Rubens, Michael.

562
00:42:23,380 --> 00:42:25,480
你的巴勒斯坦人民解放組織護照
Your Front for the Liberation of Palestine passport.

563
00:42:25,480 --> 00:42:27,080
-瓊 拉蒂斯 –穿過這個洞
- June, Ladis. - Go through the hole.

564
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:29,920
打開你的包 打開你的包
Open your bag. Open your bag.

565
00:42:31,050 --> 00:42:32,880
伯格曼 阿倫
Bergman, Aaron.

566
00:42:32,890 --> 00:42:35,050
快點 快點
Hurry up. Hurry up.

567
00:42:36,960 --> 00:42:38,060
這叫什麼事
What is this?

568
00:42:38,060 --> 00:42:39,060
所有人
Everybody.

569
00:42:39,060 --> 00:42:40,420
來吧 來吧 來吧
Come on, come on, come on.

570
00:42:40,430 --> 00:42:42,830
布洛赫 朵拉
Bloch, Dora.

571
00:42:45,200 --> 00:42:47,970
科恩 漢娜
Cohen, Hanna.

572
00:42:47,970 --> 00:42:49,900
不 不好意思 不不 我…我有孩子
No. Uh, excuse me. No, no, I-I have children.

573
00:42:49,900 --> 00:42:51,300
我不能離開我的孩子們
I can't leave my children.

574
00:42:51,300 --> 00:42:53,140
-快點 快點！ -我必須抗議這樣做
- Hurry up. Hurry up! - I must protest at this.

575
00:42:53,140 --> 00:42:54,970
不 你們不能這樣做 這是錯的
No, you can't be doing this. This is wrong.

576
00:42:54,970 --> 00:42:57,110
-她不能離開她的孩子 –不可能離開 –喂！喂！
- She can't leave her children. - It's impossible. - Hey, hey!

577
00:42:57,110 --> 00:42:58,940
閉嘴！坐下！
Shut up! Sit!

578
00:42:58,950 --> 00:43:00,040
還動！坐下！
Move! Down!

579
00:43:00,050 --> 00:43:02,220
坐下！坐下！閉嘴！
Down! Down! Shut up!

580
00:43:03,520 --> 00:43:05,520
我們不同意這樣做
We didn't agree to this.

581
00:43:05,520 --> 00:43:07,390
-看住乘客們 –我不是納粹
- Watch the passengers. - I'm not a Nazi.

582
00:43:07,390 --> 00:43:08,990
-看住乘客！ -喂！坐下！喂！
- Watch the passengers! - Hey! Sit down! Hey!

583
00:43:08,990 --> 00:43:10,390
我想和哈達德談談
I want to talk to Haddad.

584
00:43:10,390 --> 00:43:13,020
-以後再談 –我們得現在談
- Later. - We talk about this now.

585
00:43:13,030 --> 00:43:14,890
-我們現在就談談這事！ -看住乘客們！
- We talk about this now! - Watch the passengers.

586
00:43:14,890 --> 00:43:16,490
我們以後再說
We'll talk about this later.

587
00:43:19,400 --> 00:43:21,230
現在 他媽的把嘴閉上 所有人！
Now, shut the fuck up, all of you!

588
00:43:21,230 --> 00:43:24,370
任何想要反抗我的人都會被槍斃
Anyone who tries to resist me will be shot.

589
00:43:24,370 --> 00:43:25,940
明白嗎？
Do you understand?

590
00:43:29,010 --> 00:43:31,040
所有人 繼續
All of you. Now.

591
00:43:31,040 --> 00:43:33,310
哈圖 伊蘭
Hartuv, Ilan.

592
00:43:33,310 --> 00:43:34,810
下一個
Next.

593
00:43:38,120 --> 00:43:40,920
梅耶 薩拉
Mayet, Sala.

594
00:43:42,390 --> 00:43:44,860
梅耶 亞伯拉罕
Mayet, Abraham.

595
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:48,530
埃爾貝 莫瑞斯
Elbaz, Maurice.

596
00:43:52,600 --> 00:43:55,100
烏曼 麗貝卡
Ullman, Rebecca.

597
00:43:57,370 --> 00:44:00,170
以色列人？
Israeli?

598
00:44:00,170 --> 00:44:02,940
你為什麼有法國護照和以色列身份證？
Why do you have French passport and Israeli I.D. card?

599
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:04,980
噢 我…我是法國公民
Well, I-I'm a French citizen.

600
00:44:04,980 --> 00:44:06,340
我在以色列工作
I was working in Israel,

601
00:44:06,350 --> 00:44:08,610
所以 呃 我拿到了那張
and, uh, I've got that I.D. card,

602
00:44:08,620 --> 00:44:10,110
和我護照一起交上去的身份證
which I handed in with my passport.

603
00:44:10,120 --> 00:44:11,120
你是士兵
You are soldier.

604
00:44:11,120 --> 00:44:12,580
不 我是法國人 我 呃……
No, I'm French. I, uh...

605
00:44:12,580 --> 00:44:14,490
你是間諜
You are spy.

606
00:44:14,490 --> 00:44:16,420
等等 不 我是法國公民
Wait. No, I-I'm a French citizen.

607
00:44:16,420 --> 00:44:18,120
過來吧
All right.

608
00:44:18,120 --> 00:44:19,590
-快走 快走！ -好
- Move. Move! - Okay.

609
00:44:21,530 --> 00:44:23,230
他是法國人
He's French.

610
00:44:23,230 --> 00:44:24,900
他是你朋友？
He is your friend?

611
00:44:24,900 --> 00:44:27,030
-對 –那你也去那邊
- Yes. - Then you go through there, too.

612
00:44:33,640 --> 00:44:35,510
為了這項計劃的成功
For this plan to succeed,

613
00:44:35,510 --> 00:44:37,440
我們必須動用足夠的軍事力量
we need to use a big enough force

614
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:39,540
來奪取機場的控制權
to seize control of the airport.

615
00:44:39,550 --> 00:44:42,650
首先 我們動用突擊隊員 殺死恐怖分子
First, we use the commandos, kill the terrorists,

616
00:44:42,650 --> 00:44:44,280
確保人質安全
secure the hostages.

617
00:44:44,280 --> 00:44:47,050
然後我們空運增援部隊
Then we fly in reinforcements.

618
00:44:47,050 --> 00:44:50,920
包括重型武器 至少1000個士兵
Heavy weaponry, at least 1,000 men.

619
00:44:52,290 --> 00:44:54,330
西蒙 你要入侵烏干達？
You want to invade Uganda, Shimon?

620
00:44:54,330 --> 00:44:58,400
哦 我們離開的時候再還給他們
Oh, we give it back to them when we leave.

621
00:44:58,400 --> 00:45:00,530
我們不能入侵一個聯合國
We cannot invade a country that is a member

622
00:45:00,530 --> 00:45:02,670
和及非洲聯盟成員國
of the UN and the African League.

623
00:45:02,670 --> 00:45:05,970
並且運輸這麼大規模的部隊是不可能的
And it's impossible to move a force of that size

624
00:45:05,970 --> 00:45:07,270
4000公里的秘密潛入
4,000 kilometers undetected.

625
00:45:07,270 --> 00:45:09,110
我們必須行動
We have to act.

626
00:45:09,110 --> 00:45:12,040
絕不與恐怖分子談判
There can be no negotiations with terrorists.

627
00:45:12,050 --> 00:45:14,610
我正在和參謀長談話 西蒙
I'm talking to the chief of staff, Shimon.

628
00:45:14,610 --> 00:45:16,980
軍人 而不是政客
The soldier, not the politician.

629
00:45:16,980 --> 00:45:20,250
我必須同意總理的意見
I have to agree with the prime minister.

630
00:45:20,250 --> 00:45:22,450
我們需要查出阿明 是否在幫助他們
We need to find out if Amin is helping them.

631
00:45:22,450 --> 00:45:25,020
你去過烏干達 對吧？你和他打過交道？
You were in Uganda, right? You dealt with him?

632
00:45:25,020 --> 00:45:27,120
我訓練過他的軍隊 是的
I trained his army, yes.

633
00:45:27,130 --> 00:45:31,000
我寧願假設他不會向法國宣戰
I'd like to assume he's not gonna declare war on France.

634
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:34,000
話雖如此 這人絕對是瘋了
Having said that, the man is absolutely crazy.

635
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:37,370
他可能有想法 某種野心
He might have a dream, some kind of a vision,

636
00:45:37,370 --> 00:45:40,400
任何事都有可能發生
and anything can happen.

637
00:45:40,410 --> 00:45:43,080
我可以試著打給他
I can try... call him.

638
00:45:44,540 --> 00:45:46,480
如果阿明 在恐怖分子一邊
If Amin is on the terrorists' side,

639
00:45:46,480 --> 00:45:48,480
我們可能不得不進行談判
we may have to negotiate.

640
00:45:48,480 --> 00:45:53,250
總理 他們要求釋放52名恐怖分子
Prime Minister, they are asking for 52 terrorists.

641
00:45:53,250 --> 00:45:55,750
以色列人不能投降 決不
Israel cannot capitulate. It cannot.

642
00:45:55,760 --> 00:45:57,720
他們後天起將開始
They're going to start killing the hostages

643
00:45:57,720 --> 00:46:00,220
殺害人質
the day after tomorrow.

644
00:46:00,230 --> 00:46:01,460
打給阿明
Call Amin.

645
00:46:01,460 --> 00:46:03,160
我想知道他的立場
I want to know where he stands.

646
00:46:05,800 --> 00:46:07,750
總統官邸

647
00:46:08,300 --> 00:46:10,170
他們已經把猶太人集中
They have moved the Jews together

648
00:46:10,170 --> 00:46:12,170
在恩德培老航站樓了
at the old terminal at Entebbe.

649
00:46:12,170 --> 00:46:15,570
他們用烈性炸葯把人質集中起來
They have surrounded them with high explosives.

650
00:46:15,580 --> 00:46:19,580
在飛機上和航站樓周圍都有TNT炸葯
They have TNT on the plane and all around the building,

651
00:46:19,580 --> 00:46:21,450
甚至他們身上也有
even on their bodies.

652
00:46:21,450 --> 00:46:25,620
他們說他們將與人質一起自殺
They said that they will commit suicide with the hostages.

653
00:46:25,620 --> 00:46:29,020
告訴你們政府 我無能為力
Tell your government there is nothing I can do.

654
00:46:29,020 --> 00:46:31,250
但是 閣下 這是在你們國家
But, Your Excellency, this is your country.

655
00:46:31,260 --> 00:46:32,660
你有一個機會
You have an opportunity

656
00:46:32,660 --> 00:46:35,630
作為英雄被載入史冊
to go down in history as a great man.

657
00:46:35,630 --> 00:46:37,230
救了那些人質的英雄
The man who saved these people.

658
00:46:37,230 --> 00:46:39,430
這是一個上帝賜予你的
This is a-a great opportunity, sir,

659
00:46:39,430 --> 00:46:41,030
極好的機會
given to you by God.

660
00:46:41,030 --> 00:46:43,130
那些恐怖分子想要你們
All the terrorists want is for you

661
00:46:43,140 --> 00:46:45,400
把你們的囚犯送到這裡來
to send your prisoners here.

662
00:46:45,410 --> 00:46:48,980
不要聽坐在那你旁邊的巴勒斯坦人民解放組織的人
Don't listen to those from the PFLP sitting beside you.

663
00:46:51,380 --> 00:46:53,480
你在冒犯我 老朋友
You are offending me, old friend.

664
00:46:53,480 --> 00:46:55,350
我試圖做的就是
All I'm trying to do

665
00:46:55,350 --> 00:46:57,750
確保人質安全
is make sure the hostages are safe.

666
00:46:57,750 --> 00:46:59,280
很抱歉 閣下
I'm sorry, Your Excellency,

667
00:46:59,280 --> 00:47:01,820
但是請考慮一下我說的話
but please consider what I'm saying.

668
00:47:01,820 --> 00:47:05,320
不要錯過這個機會
Don't miss this opportunity

669
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:07,360
向那些說你壞話的人展現
to show the people who say bad things about you

670
00:47:07,360 --> 00:47:08,630
您是個多麼偉大的人
what a great man you are.

671
00:47:08,630 --> 00:47:10,730
實際上 我…我想這會
Actually, I-I think this will

672
00:47:10,730 --> 00:47:12,500
使你獲得諾貝爾和平獎的
get you the Nobel Prize for peace.

673
00:47:16,640 --> 00:47:18,700
呃 閣下？
Uh, Y-Your Highness?

674
00:47:20,840 --> 00:47:22,480
閣下？
Y-Your Highness?

675
00:47:27,480 --> 00:47:29,380
為什麼巴勒斯坦人民解放組織想要我們
Why would the PFLP want us

676
00:47:29,380 --> 00:47:31,220
把他們的囚犯送到烏干達？
to fly their prisoners to Uganda?

677
00:47:31,220 --> 00:47:34,450
我認為這是阿明的主意 不是巴勒斯坦人的
I think that's Amin, not the Palestinians.

678
00:47:34,450 --> 00:47:36,690
人質被釋放的時候他想在場
He wants to be there when the prisoners are released.

679
00:47:36,690 --> 00:47:38,820
他想告訴蘇聯人和阿拉伯人
He wants to show the Soviets and the Arabs

680
00:47:38,830 --> 00:47:40,660
現在他和他們是一夥的
that he is with them now.

681
00:47:40,660 --> 00:47:44,560
他想獲得他們的認同 他們的支持 他們的武器
He wants their approval, their support, their arms.

682
00:47:44,560 --> 00:47:46,630
還有500萬塊錢
The $5 million.

683
00:47:46,630 --> 00:47:48,630
如果烏干達人與恐怖分子達成一致
If the Ugandans are with the terrorists,

684
00:47:48,630 --> 00:47:51,170
麻煩就更大了
this operation will have to be even bigger.

685
00:47:51,170 --> 00:47:53,370
我和基辛格談過
I spoke to Kissinger.

686
00:47:53,370 --> 00:47:56,170
他說人質都死了
He said it's better if everybody dies

687
00:47:56,180 --> 00:47:58,210
也比我們談判要好
than we negotiate.

688
00:47:58,210 --> 00:48:00,380
好吧 如果這跟法國沒什麼關係
Yeah, well, if it's not a French problem,

689
00:48:00,380 --> 00:48:03,880
那它更不關美國什麼事  西蒙
then it's even less of an American problem, Shimon.

690
00:48:03,880 --> 00:48:07,250
我們就盡自己所能吧
Let's do the only thing we can do.

691
00:48:07,250 --> 00:48:09,220
不 請等一下
No, wait. Please.

692
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:12,760
伊扎克
Yitzhak.

693
00:48:14,530 --> 00:48:17,790
西蒙 我跟你解釋下目前的情況
Shimon, let me explain the situation as it stands.

694
00:48:17,800 --> 00:48:19,430
我們沒有情報
We have no intelligence.

695
00:48:19,430 --> 00:48:21,530
我們只知道人質在舊航站樓裡
We only know the hostages are in the terminal.

696
00:48:21,530 --> 00:48:22,830
其他什麼都不知道
Nothing else.

697
00:48:22,830 --> 00:48:24,570
如果他們昨晚把人質轉移了呢
What if they moved them around last night?

698
00:48:24,570 --> 00:48:26,140
如果現在有人
What if now we have people sitting

699
00:48:26,140 --> 00:48:27,910
正拿著槍和手榴彈坐他們中間呢
in the middle of them with guns and grenades?

700
00:48:27,910 --> 00:48:29,570
一旦他們知道我們正在接近
As soon as they know we're coming,

701
00:48:29,580 --> 00:48:32,280
他們就會開始殺戮  男人... 女人... 小孩...
they start to kill the men, the women, the children.

702
00:48:32,280 --> 00:48:35,650
所以他們在挑著猶太人 而你只想著談判
So they are selecting Jews, and you want to negotiate.

703
00:48:38,780 --> 00:48:40,850
西蒙...
Shimon...

704
00:48:40,850 --> 00:48:43,320
如果我們不談判   如果我們永遠都不談判
if we don't negotiate, if we never negotiate,

705
00:48:43,320 --> 00:48:45,320
如果我們總是處在戰爭狀態
if we're always at war,

706
00:48:45,320 --> 00:48:47,190
那我們就會把我們的國家變成一座監獄
then we will make our country a prison,

707
00:48:47,190 --> 00:48:50,160
每個人都是囚犯
and every one of our citizens will be a prisoner.

708
00:48:50,160 --> 00:48:52,300
我們的敵人就是我們的鄰居
Our enemies are our neighbors.

709
00:48:52,300 --> 00:48:54,270
我們不可能擺脫他們
We can't get away from them.

710
00:48:54,270 --> 00:48:58,140
總有一天 我們要為了和平而談判
One day, we have to talk and to make peace.

711
00:49:01,340 --> 00:49:03,610
謝謝 先生們
Thank you, gentlemen.

712
00:49:10,420 --> 00:49:12,580
他們怎麼知道你在這
How did they know you were here?

713
00:49:12,580 --> 00:49:13,920
他猜的吧
He guessed.

714
00:49:13,920 --> 00:49:15,920
神靈警告過我的母親
The spirits warned my mother

715
00:49:15,920 --> 00:49:17,920
我不應該冒犯以色列人
I should never offend the Israelis.

716
00:49:17,920 --> 00:49:19,590
我們應該聽我母親的
We should listen to my mother.

717
00:49:19,590 --> 00:49:21,190
什麼意思
To your mother?

718
00:49:22,700 --> 00:49:24,730
先放一些人質
Release some of the hostages.

719
00:49:24,730 --> 00:49:26,500
這樣可以安撫法國人
It will appease the French

720
00:49:26,500 --> 00:49:28,500
也能讓我們的計劃更順利
and make things easier at the airport.

721
00:49:35,760 --> 00:49:37,220
我不覺得他是間諜

722
00:49:50,320 --> 00:49:51,820
他們在折磨他

723
00:49:53,190 --> 00:49:54,530
我來這不是當保安的

724
00:49:54,740 --> 00:49:56,030
別抱怨了

725
00:49:57,990 --> 00:49:59,450
他們把我們往局外擠

726
00:50:01,080 --> 00:50:02,910
他們總是忽視我

727
00:50:03,120 --> 00:50:04,370
在維也納和石油輸出國組織一起的時候

728
00:50:04,580 --> 00:50:05,550
卡洛斯沒選我

729
00:50:05,750 --> 00:50:06,750
我不只是個賣書的

730
00:50:07,250 --> 00:50:09,920
你賣書都賣不好

731
00:50:15,970 --> 00:50:17,550
你得對他們寬容點

732
00:50:17,750 --> 00:50:19,220
你也太寬容了

733
00:50:19,430 --> 00:50:20,970
他們不需要理解我們 他們覺得我們是納粹分子

734
00:50:21,180 --> 00:50:22,680
他們是猶太人 我們是德國人

735
00:50:22,890 --> 00:50:24,640
他們當然覺得我們是納粹分子

736
00:50:24,850 --> 00:50:26,390
不然你以為呢？

737
00:50:26,600 --> 00:50:27,730
期望他們理解我們？

738
00:50:27,930 --> 00:50:29,980
當個納粹 他們至少還會害怕

739
00:50:30,190 --> 00:50:31,650
放屁

740
00:50:31,850 --> 00:50:33,650
我才不假扮納粹

741
00:50:34,950 --> 00:50:35,900
操你媽

742
00:50:36,110 --> 00:50:36,900
安靜點

743
00:50:42,810 --> 00:50:44,280
他媽的
Scheisse.

744
00:50:45,930 --> 00:50:47,410
你已經吃三次了

745
00:50:48,980 --> 00:50:51,170
自從我們來這你就沒睡過

746
00:50:53,390 --> 00:50:54,840
我自己來

747
00:50:57,370 --> 00:50:59,300
這

748
00:50:59,500 --> 00:51:00,840
再吃一顆

749
00:51:01,040 --> 00:51:02,850
好樣的

750
00:52:03,990 --> 00:52:04,990
這兒
Here.

751
00:52:06,090 --> 00:52:07,890
這就是阿明的車
This is Idi Amin's car.

752
00:52:07,890 --> 00:52:10,460
現在 烏干達的所有官員
Now, all the officials in Uganda

753
00:52:10,460 --> 00:52:12,060
都用一輛黑色的梅賽德斯豪華轎車代步
use a black Mercedes limousine.

754
00:52:12,060 --> 00:52:13,460
嗯
Right.

755
00:52:13,470 --> 00:52:15,600
如果我們用這個接近舊航站樓
If we approached the terminal in one,

756
00:52:15,600 --> 00:52:16,770
恐怖分子可能會認為是阿明
the terrorists would think Amin

757
00:52:16,770 --> 00:52:18,140
來和人質交談
is coming to talk to the hostages.

758
00:52:18,140 --> 00:52:20,670
這樣給了我們一個機會製造「驚喜」
That gives us the element of surprise.

759
00:52:20,670 --> 00:52:23,640
給我一輛奔馳 我們會完成這個任務
Get me a limo there, we'll get the job done.

760
00:52:23,640 --> 00:52:24,640
本尼
Benny?

761
00:52:24,640 --> 00:52:26,610
你怎麼看
What do you think?

762
00:52:26,610 --> 00:52:29,680
我們可以把奔馳放在大力士運輸機裡
We can put the Mercedes in a Hercules

763
00:52:29,680 --> 00:52:30,980
還有特種部隊人員
with Sayeret Matkal,

764
00:52:30,980 --> 00:52:33,020
飛機會停在新航站樓
land the plane at the new terminal.

765
00:52:33,020 --> 00:52:34,550
- 嗯 - 他們可以開著奔馳
- Good. - They drive the Mercedes

766
00:52:34,550 --> 00:52:37,990
去舊航站樓殺死恐怖分子
to the old terminal, kill the terrorists,

767
00:52:37,990 --> 00:52:41,560
把人質安放在飛機裡 然後飛回來
put the hostages on a plane, fly back.

768
00:52:41,560 --> 00:52:42,990
- 很好 - 現在 為了做到這一步
- Perfect. - Now, to do that,

769
00:52:42,990 --> 00:52:44,660
我們需要控制整個區域
we need to control the whole area.

770
00:52:44,660 --> 00:52:45,930
兩個航站樓都要控制
Both terminals.

771
00:52:45,930 --> 00:52:48,630
那你需要什麼
And what do you need?

772
00:52:48,630 --> 00:52:51,740
三個小隊...
Three companies of soldiers...

773
00:52:51,740 --> 00:52:53,540
丹... 拜託了
Dan, please.

774
00:52:53,540 --> 00:52:55,570
兩個小隊
Two companies of soldiers,

775
00:52:55,570 --> 00:52:57,540
還有裝甲和重型武器
armor and heavy weapons.

776
00:52:57,540 --> 00:52:59,080
- 那得要四駕飛機 - 對 快速行動
- That will be four planes. - Right. Move fast.

777
00:52:59,080 --> 00:53:00,980
所有單位要保持警惕
Keep all units on alert.

778
00:53:00,980 --> 00:53:02,880
拉賓已經和法國人協商過了
Rabin is already talking to the French.

779
00:53:02,880 --> 00:53:05,150
好的 我們有新任務了 快來
Okay, we have new orders. Come down.

780
00:53:05,150 --> 00:53:06,990
走吧
Let's go.

781
00:53:11,480 --> 00:53:13,020
第四日

782
00:53:13,220 --> 00:53:17,420
1976年 6月30日 星期三

783
00:53:15,560 --> 00:53:17,630
好 好
Yes, yes.

784
00:53:17,630 --> 00:53:19,100
請上車
Please.

785
00:53:19,100 --> 00:53:21,560
祝你們旅途愉快
We wish you a pleasant journey.

786
00:53:21,570 --> 00:53:24,570
快來上車 快上車
Come and enter the bus. Enter the bus.

787
00:53:26,570 --> 00:53:29,610
當你們到達目的地的時候
And when you arrive at your destination,

788
00:53:29,610 --> 00:53:31,680
請告訴他們
please tell them

789
00:53:31,680 --> 00:53:35,110
烏干達總統保障了你們的安全
that the president of Uganda guaranteed your safety.

790
00:53:35,110 --> 00:53:37,180
啊 修女 我是你的朋友
Ah. Mother, I'm your friend.

791
00:53:37,180 --> 00:53:39,780
- 請為我們祈禱 - 我不想走
- Please say a prayer for us. - I don't want to leave.

792
00:53:39,780 --> 00:53:42,190
我想把我的座位讓給那些
I would like to offer my place to one of the Israeli people

793
00:53:42,190 --> 00:53:43,620
被挾持的以色列人民
who are being held.

794
00:53:44,860 --> 00:53:46,720
那是不可能的
That will not be possible.

795
00:53:46,720 --> 00:53:48,860
我沒打算走
I am not going to go.

796
00:53:48,860 --> 00:53:50,830
請上車
Please get inside the bus.

797
00:53:50,830 --> 00:53:53,700
不 我不打算走
No, I'm not going to go.

798
00:53:55,470 --> 00:53:56,670
她糊塗了
She's confused.

799
00:53:56,670 --> 00:53:58,670
快幫她上車
Please help her get inside the bus.

800
00:53:58,670 --> 00:54:00,700
- 不 我要留下來 - 幫她上車
- No. I'm going to stay. - Help her.

801
00:54:00,710 --> 00:54:01,970
- 讓她上車 - 上車吧 女士
- Help her. - Get in, madam.

802
00:54:01,970 --> 00:54:04,070
- 不 我..我想留下來 - 上去 快上車
- No, I-I want to stay. - Get in. Get in.

803
00:54:04,080 --> 00:54:05,940
求你了 我..我想留下來
Please. I-I want to stay.

804
00:54:05,950 --> 00:54:06,910
- 拜託了 - 上車
- Please. - Get in.

805
00:54:44,250 --> 00:54:45,850
沙羅
Shalom.

806
00:54:49,760 --> 00:54:53,590
恐怕我不是來帶來好消息的
I am afraid I'm not the bearer of glad tidings.

807
00:54:53,590 --> 00:54:56,560
我保證我會盡我所能
I promised I would do everything in my power

808
00:54:56,560 --> 00:54:58,860
讓你們被放出去
to have you released.

809
00:54:58,860 --> 00:55:01,870
但是他們還沒有收到你們政府的消息
But they haven't heard from your government yet.

810
00:55:01,870 --> 00:55:05,100
最後期限是24小時
The deadline is 24 hours away.

811
00:55:05,100 --> 00:55:07,640
我很擔心你們
I'm very worried about you.

812
00:55:09,110 --> 00:55:13,580
這些人與你們無冤無仇
These men bear no grudge against you.

813
00:55:13,580 --> 00:55:17,750
他們只恨你們法西斯式的以色列政府
Only against your fascist Israeli government.

814
00:55:17,750 --> 00:55:22,620
但是如果你們的政府不談判的話
But if your government do not negotiate,

815
00:55:22,620 --> 00:55:26,560
他們會殺死兩個孩子
they will kill two children

816
00:55:26,560 --> 00:55:28,630
每24小時
every 24 hours.

817
00:55:35,700 --> 00:55:37,900
就從這兩個孩子開始
Starting with these two.

818
00:55:45,140 --> 00:55:46,810
你怎麼能做得到
How can you do this?

819
00:55:46,810 --> 00:55:49,350
拿著你的機槍站在這裡
Standing here with your machine gun.

820
00:55:49,350 --> 00:55:51,520
他們還都是些小孩子
These are little children.

821
00:55:53,020 --> 00:55:54,720
我們有士兵
We have soldiers.

822
00:55:54,720 --> 00:55:57,090
如果你想要戰鬥 去找我們的士兵
If you have to fight, you fight our soldiers.

823
00:56:08,130 --> 00:56:09,930
我不想喝咖啡
I don't want a coffee.

824
00:56:09,930 --> 00:56:12,140
齊夫 你有個電話
Zeev, you have a phone call.

825
00:56:12,140 --> 00:56:14,200
真希望首演的時候我能在
Just wish I could be there.

826
00:56:14,210 --> 00:56:16,710
你不能來嗎？
You can't make it?

827
00:56:16,710 --> 00:56:18,080
我剋服恐懼了
I got the part I wanted.

828
00:56:18,080 --> 00:56:19,610
嘿 那很好啊
Hey, that's great.

829
00:56:19,610 --> 00:56:21,610
我為你感到高興
I'm happy for you.

830
00:56:21,610 --> 00:56:23,850
你會安全嗎
Will you be safe?

831
00:56:23,850 --> 00:56:26,550
別談這個
Don't want to talk about that.

832
00:56:28,090 --> 00:56:30,220
你有一直想我嗎
Have you been thinking of me?

833
00:56:33,190 --> 00:56:35,160
沒 我的意思是.. 你知道..
No, I mean, you know, it...

834
00:56:37,400 --> 00:56:41,370
薩拉  有時候 你愛的人...
Sarah, people you love, sometimes...

835
00:56:41,370 --> 00:56:44,900
想著你愛的人 嗯...其實...
thinking of them, it, um...

836
00:56:44,900 --> 00:56:46,840
沒什麼用
it doesn't help.

837
00:56:50,680 --> 00:56:52,380
是啊
Yeah.

838
00:56:52,380 --> 00:56:54,310
知道了
I know what you mean.

839
00:57:08,890 --> 00:57:10,860
你在射擊場練射擊了嗎
Have you been practicing on your shooting range?

840
00:57:10,860 --> 00:57:11,860
練了
Yes.

841
00:57:12,970 --> 00:57:14,260
每天都在練
Every day.

842
00:57:14,270 --> 00:57:16,400
很好
Good.

843
00:57:16,400 --> 00:57:18,400
誰的電話
Who was that?

844
00:57:18,400 --> 00:57:20,100
我女朋友
It was my girlfriend.

845
00:57:20,100 --> 00:57:21,970
她是軍人嗎
Is she in the military?

846
00:57:21,970 --> 00:57:23,680
不 她不是
No, she's not.

847
00:57:25,880 --> 00:57:28,140
如果你想和她在一起
If you want to be with her,

848
00:57:28,150 --> 00:57:30,380
你得讓她參軍
you need to get her to join the army.

849
00:57:30,380 --> 00:57:32,280
否則 你最好離她遠點
Otherwise, it's better you leave her alone.

850
00:57:32,280 --> 00:57:33,850
你什麼意思
What do you mean?

851
00:57:33,850 --> 00:57:35,920
字面意思
I mean exactly what I said.

852
00:57:35,920 --> 00:57:37,820
相信我 有經驗
Trust me, I know.

853
00:57:39,930 --> 00:57:42,430
巴勒斯坦的劫機人員
The Palestinian hijackers

854
00:57:42,430 --> 00:57:46,230
釋放了48名人質乘客
released 48 of their hostage airline passengers.

855
00:57:46,230 --> 00:57:48,970
但他們緊張地拿著機槍站在
But they stood nervously holding machine guns

856
00:57:48,970 --> 00:57:52,770
剩下的209名人質身邊  威脅著要殺死他們
on the remaining 209 and threatened to kill them all

857
00:57:52,770 --> 00:57:54,740
炸毀法國客機
and to blow up the French airliner

858
00:57:54,740 --> 00:57:56,740
除非以色列政府滿足他們的要求
unless their demands are met.

859
00:57:56,740 --> 00:57:59,880
放走的48名乘客是去巴黎的
The 48 passengers they let go left for Paris,

860
00:57:59,880 --> 00:58:02,110
不久前剛剛抵達
where they arrived a short time ago.

861
00:58:02,110 --> 00:58:04,410
約翰·帕爾瑪那時候在機場
John Palmer was there at the airport.

862
00:58:04,420 --> 00:58:07,120
奧利機場的VIP休息室
The VIP lounge here at Orly Airport

863
00:58:07,120 --> 00:58:09,250
已經被警方封鎖
has been cordoned off by police,

864
00:58:09,250 --> 00:58:11,220
裡面的等候室
and the waiting room inside

865
00:58:11,220 --> 00:58:13,790
擠滿了人質的親屬和朋友
crowded with many relatives and friends

866
00:58:13,790 --> 00:58:16,830
等著接回新釋放的人質
waiting to greet the newly released hostages.

867
00:58:16,830 --> 00:58:19,500
當然 這些人質都在這架飛機上
Many of them, of course, all of them on this flight,

868
00:58:19,500 --> 00:58:23,870
他們想著能活下來可真幸運
consider themselves very lucky indeed to be alive.

869
00:58:23,790 --> 00:58:25,330
第五日

870
00:58:25,530 --> 00:58:28,590
1976年 7月1日 星期四

871
00:58:30,410 --> 00:58:31,940
借過一下
Excuse me.

872
00:58:32,630 --> 00:58:33,550
怎麼了

873
00:58:33,750 --> 00:58:36,760
不知道 什麼都用不起 沒水 廁所也壞了

874
00:58:43,390 --> 00:58:44,640
骯髒的德國人

875
00:59:11,050 --> 00:59:13,450
你必須知道你們做的事對世界其他地方的影響
You must know how this looks to the rest of the world.

876
00:59:13,450 --> 00:59:14,480
是
Yeah.

877
00:59:14,490 --> 00:59:17,150
我知道會產生什麼影響
I know how this looks.

878
00:59:17,160 --> 00:59:18,990
但影響是影響 現實是現實
But it's not the reality.

879
00:59:21,160 --> 00:59:24,830
我不對我同胞的行為負責任
I'm not responsible for the actions of my compatriots.

880
00:59:24,830 --> 00:59:26,200
你在重蹈他們的覆轍
You are repeating their actions.

881
00:59:26,200 --> 00:59:28,560
不 我不是 我不是剝削者
No, I'm not. I'm not the oppressor.

882
00:59:28,570 --> 00:59:30,500
我認為巴勒斯坦人民應當擁有權利
I believe in the rights of the Palestinian people.

883
00:59:30,500 --> 00:59:32,470
他們失去了家園
They have no homeland.

884
00:59:32,470 --> 00:59:34,940
你去過巴勒斯坦難民營嗎?
Have you ever seen a Palestinian refugee camp?

885
00:59:34,940 --> 00:59:37,010
你見過人們是如何苟活的嗎?
Have you seen how these people live?

886
00:59:37,010 --> 00:59:38,810
你見過他們的孩子嗎?
Have you seen their children?

887
00:59:38,810 --> 00:59:41,950
所以為了他們你願意
So, for them, you are willing

888
00:59:41,950 --> 00:59:44,480
消滅下麵那些人?
to exterminate those people down there?

889
00:59:47,020 --> 00:59:48,920
我們得幫他們
We have to help them.

890
00:59:52,520 --> 00:59:55,390
你是乾什麼的? 做什麼工作?
What do you do? What's your job?

891
00:59:55,390 --> 00:59:57,200
你不是士兵
You're not a soldier.

892
00:59:59,460 --> 01:00:01,460
我是出版商
I'm a publisher.

893
01:00:01,470 --> 01:00:03,930
我出版革命書籍
I publish revolutionary texts.

894
01:00:03,940 --> 01:00:06,140
你有沒有出版過關於通管道的書?
Have you ever published any books about plumbing?

895
01:00:07,910 --> 01:00:10,180
還沒有
Not yet.

896
01:00:11,940 --> 01:00:14,210
尊嚴...
Dignity...

897
01:00:14,210 --> 01:00:16,610
是眾之所望
is all people want.

898
01:00:16,620 --> 01:00:18,990
唯有獲得自由才能取得尊嚴
Dignity comes when you're free.

899
01:00:22,450 --> 01:00:26,060
自來水使你獲得自由
Running water makes you free.

900
01:00:26,060 --> 01:00:28,260
廁所...
Toilet...

901
01:00:28,260 --> 01:00:30,030
讓你獲得自由
makes you free.

902
01:00:32,530 --> 01:00:36,030
一個水管工抵十個革命家
One plumber is worth ten revolutionaries.

903
01:00:41,540 --> 01:00:44,440
你有沒有想過你是在浪費生命
Do you ever think you're wasting your life?

904
01:00:46,010 --> 01:00:48,010
沒有
No.

905
01:00:48,010 --> 01:00:49,510
你呢?
Do you?

906
01:00:51,380 --> 01:00:53,320
我是個工程師
I'm an engineer.

907
01:00:53,320 --> 01:00:54,650
我能製造物品
I can make things.

908
01:00:54,650 --> 01:00:58,160
一個工程師抵50個革命家
One engineer is worth 50 revolutionaries.

909
01:01:04,650 --> 01:01:07,050
我不想讓博斯單獨跟乘客待著

910
01:01:07,290 --> 01:01:08,330
他變得越來越大意了

911
01:01:08,530 --> 01:01:09,580
他覺得這一切都是遊戲

912
01:01:09,780 --> 01:01:11,870
如果你被困著跟他一起站崗 這就不是遊戲了

913
01:01:12,430 --> 01:01:13,920
你一晚上都得聽他嘮叨

914
01:01:14,130 --> 01:01:15,420
世界的革命

915
01:01:15,620 --> 01:01:16,960
巴勒斯坦的革命

916
01:01:17,160 --> 01:01:18,840
一直不停

917
01:01:22,670 --> 01:01:24,690
你覺得以色利人會來嗎

918
01:01:24,810 --> 01:01:26,300
我們已經把他們逼入絕境了

919
01:01:28,750 --> 01:01:30,430
如果他們來了 那殺死他們對不對呢

920
01:01:30,640 --> 01:01:32,140
他們殺了我的孩子

921
01:01:32,690 --> 01:01:34,320
賈貝爾 這什麼情況?
Jaber. What is this?

922
01:01:34,330 --> 01:01:36,160
度假營嗎?
A holiday camp now?

923
01:01:36,160 --> 01:01:37,900
他們是孩子 哈里曼
They are children, Halima.

924
01:01:46,040 --> 01:01:47,500
以色列政府
The pressure on

925
01:01:47,510 --> 01:01:49,070
所面臨的壓力是巨大的
the Israeli government was tremendous,

926
01:01:49,070 --> 01:01:50,610
尤其是來自國民的壓力
especially from within the country.

927
01:01:50,610 --> 01:01:52,540
以色列人質的親屬
Relatives of the Israeli hostages

928
01:01:52,540 --> 01:01:54,240
於今天上午
held an emotional meeting

929
01:01:54,250 --> 01:01:56,250
和政府代表舉行了會晤
with government representatives this morning.

930
01:01:56,250 --> 01:01:58,720
他們不在乎以色列的一個基本國策
They didn't care that Israel has a basic policy

931
01:01:58,720 --> 01:02:00,980
那就是不和恐怖分子做交易
of not dealing with terrorists.

932
01:02:00,990 --> 01:02:02,350
今天早晨
Late in the morning,

933
01:02:02,350 --> 01:02:03,650
他們衝進了政府大樓
they stormed the government compound,

934
01:02:03,660 --> 01:02:04,820
擊垮了軍事警察
overwhelming military police,

935
01:02:04,820 --> 01:02:07,520
試圖找到總理拉賓
in an effort to get at Prime Minister Rabin

936
01:02:07,530 --> 01:02:09,260
並告訴他他們的想法
and tell him what they thought.

937
01:02:12,460 --> 01:02:14,400
我們訴求結果! 我們不能把他們留在那兒!
We want answers! We cannot leave them there!

938
01:02:24,280 --> 01:02:26,440
家屬想讓我們釋放人質
The families want the hostages released.

939
01:02:26,450 --> 01:02:28,210
但作為一個以色列政客
But as an Israeli politician,

940
01:02:28,210 --> 01:02:31,680
你不能和恐怖分子談判
you can't afford to negotiate with terrorists.

941
01:02:31,680 --> 01:02:33,420
對
That's right.

942
01:02:33,420 --> 01:02:35,150
這成就了我
That's what I've become.

943
01:02:35,150 --> 01:02:36,420
總理!
Prime Minister!

944
01:02:36,420 --> 01:02:39,360
拉賓總理!
Prime Minister Rabin!

945
01:02:39,360 --> 01:02:40,690
我們想和總理交談
We want to speak with the prime minister.

946
01:02:40,690 --> 01:02:43,460
-停! -我們要求和總理交涉!
- Stop! - We want to speak with the prime minister.

947
01:02:43,460 --> 01:02:44,690
他欠我們一個解釋
He owes us an explanation.

948
01:02:44,700 --> 01:02:46,700
我們想見總理
We want to see the prime minister.

949
01:02:46,700 --> 01:02:48,430
等著
Wait here.

950
01:02:50,430 --> 01:02:53,300
所有人 安靜
Everybody, calm down.

951
01:02:58,210 --> 01:03:00,380
我們想要一個解釋!
We need an explanation!

952
01:03:18,700 --> 01:03:22,370
大使先生 我是總理
Mr. Ambassador, this is the prime minister.

953
01:03:22,370 --> 01:03:24,730
你去告訴法國政府
I would like you to tell the French

954
01:03:24,740 --> 01:03:28,570
我們將和恐怖分子做交易
that we're going to make an offer to the terrorists.

955
01:03:28,570 --> 01:03:30,740
讓人震驚的是 以色列人今天
To everyone's surprise, the Israelis today

956
01:03:30,740 --> 01:03:32,640
改變了一貫的政策
reversed their normal policy

957
01:03:32,640 --> 01:03:35,350
並同意和劫持者進行談判
and agreed to negotiate with the hijackers.

958
01:03:35,350 --> 01:03:38,680
劫持者將截止日期延遲至星期日上午8時
The hijackers put off their deadline to 8:00 a.m. Sunday

959
01:03:38,680 --> 01:03:41,180
就在以色列打破長期政策
after Israel broke its long-standing policy

960
01:03:41,190 --> 01:03:42,620
並同意談判之後
and agreed to negotiate.

961
01:03:42,620 --> 01:03:44,290
以色列的意見分歧
The difference of opinion in Israel

962
01:03:44,290 --> 01:03:46,420
並不在於是否釋放人質
is not over whether the hostages should be released,

963
01:03:46,430 --> 01:03:48,660
而在於從監獄釋放恐怖分子
but over whether releasing terrorists from jail here

964
01:03:48,660 --> 01:03:50,590
的代價是否過高
is too high a price to pay for it.

965
01:03:50,600 --> 01:03:53,760
今晚 西牆和眾多猶太教堂
Tonight, a special series of prayers began

966
01:03:53,760 --> 01:03:56,270
進行了一系列特別的禱告
at the Western Wall and at most synagogues.

967
01:03:56,270 --> 01:03:58,670
祈禱政府能夠
Prayers which expressed the hope that the government

968
01:03:58,670 --> 01:04:00,770
對談判做出正確的決定
made the right decision on the negotiations

969
01:04:00,770 --> 01:04:02,640
以及以色列和猶太人的人質
and that the Israeli and Jewish hostages

970
01:04:02,640 --> 01:04:05,680
會從烏干達安全返回
will indeed come out of Uganda safely.

971
01:04:19,330 --> 01:04:20,600
我們成功了

972
01:04:21,900 --> 01:04:23,230
真的成功了

973
01:04:24,600 --> 01:04:26,860
能做成功這種任務真是難以想像

974
01:04:27,070 --> 01:04:28,440
賈博認為他們在耍花招

975
01:04:28,640 --> 01:04:30,110
不是花招

976
01:04:31,170 --> 01:04:32,820
我們會改寫歷史的

977
01:04:33,840 --> 01:04:35,990
我們再也沒法回家了

978
01:04:36,210 --> 01:04:36,950
現在還不能

979
01:04:37,140 --> 01:04:38,910
不 是永遠不能了

980
01:04:39,790 --> 01:04:40,920
你覺得巴格達怎麼樣

981
01:04:41,120 --> 01:04:44,250
你完全不會明白一個女人在那裡活著會有多艱難

982
01:04:44,460 --> 01:04:46,710
阿拉伯人都是社會主義者

983
01:04:49,290 --> 01:04:50,510
換班了

984
01:04:56,330 --> 01:04:59,430
-你到底在搞什麼? -什麼?
- What the hell are you doing? - What?

985
01:04:59,430 --> 01:05:01,160
你把你的槍忘在了牆上
You left your gun lying on the wall.

986
01:05:01,170 --> 01:05:02,870
猶太人有可能會拿走呢
One of the Jews could have picked it up.

987
01:05:02,870 --> 01:05:04,770
放輕鬆 夥計 以色列人已經投降了
Relax, man. The Israelis have surrendered.

988
01:05:04,770 --> 01:05:06,770
他們還沒有投降
They have not surrendered.

989
01:05:06,770 --> 01:05:08,470
要是這是一個陷阱怎麼辦?
What if this is a trick?

990
01:05:08,470 --> 01:05:10,240
要是他們只是以此來拖延時間呢?
What if they are buying more time?

991
01:05:10,240 --> 01:05:12,680
-我們得做好準備 -好的 好的
- We have to be ready. - Okay, okay.

992
01:05:15,280 --> 01:05:17,220
你在這兒做什麼?
Why are you here?

993
01:05:21,250 --> 01:05:22,850
我想在群眾中
I want to throw bombs

994
01:05:22,850 --> 01:05:25,250
來一個'炸彈'般的頭腦風暴
into the consciousness of the masses.

995
01:05:25,260 --> 01:05:28,460
如果你得扔一個真的炸彈呢 我的朋友?
And what if you have to throw a real bomb, my friend?

996
01:05:28,460 --> 01:05:30,160
你殺過人嗎?
Have you killed?

997
01:05:30,160 --> 01:05:32,400
你覺得你能做到?
You think you can do it?

998
01:05:33,830 --> 01:05:37,230
你選擇拿起武器來戰鬥
You choose to pick up arms and fight.

999
01:05:37,240 --> 01:05:39,540
你選擇來到這裡
You choose to come here.

1000
01:05:39,540 --> 01:05:42,540
你本可以在歐洲過上美好地生活
You could have a nice life in Europe.

1001
01:05:42,540 --> 01:05:44,740
我希望我能過你那樣地生活
I wish I had your life.

1002
01:05:44,740 --> 01:05:46,840
我就不會拿起武器
I would not pick up a gun.

1003
01:05:46,850 --> 01:05:49,280
只有一無所有的人才會理解
Only people with nothing understand.

1004
01:05:49,280 --> 01:05:51,180
猶太人能夠理解
The Jews understand.

1005
01:05:52,680 --> 01:05:54,920
當德國人屠殺他們時
When your people massacred them,

1006
01:05:54,920 --> 01:05:58,320
倖存者一無所有
the ones who survived had nothing.

1007
01:05:58,320 --> 01:06:01,190
他們將死亡帶到巴勒斯坦
They brought their dead to Palestine.

1008
01:06:01,190 --> 01:06:03,330
他們帶來了羞恥和屈辱
They brought their shame and humiliation.

1009
01:06:05,230 --> 01:06:08,900
他們對我們做了他們所受的一切
They did what was done to them to us.

1010
01:06:08,900 --> 01:06:12,430
但我沒有對他們這樣做
But I didn't do it to them.

1011
01:06:12,440 --> 01:06:14,140
你對他們這樣做了
You did it to them.

1012
01:06:16,710 --> 01:06:19,580
你來到這裡只是因為你恨你的國家
You are here because you hate your country.

1013
01:06:19,580 --> 01:06:21,880
我來這裡是因為我愛我的國家
I'm here because I love mine.

1014
01:06:25,350 --> 01:06:27,220
你做好殺人的準備了嗎?
Are you ready to kill?

1015
01:06:28,320 --> 01:06:30,490
做好犧牲的準備了嗎?
Are you ready to die?

1016
01:06:34,560 --> 01:06:36,790
如果這個談判是一個騙局
If this negotiation is a trick,

1017
01:06:36,800 --> 01:06:38,730
我們立馬殺出去
we start killing immediately.

1018
01:06:41,700 --> 01:06:43,600
立馬
Immediately.

1019
01:07:02,990 --> 01:07:05,250
我們可以低空飛越紅海
We can fly down over the Red Sea

1020
01:07:05,260 --> 01:07:07,490
以躲開受到敵方雷達的檢測
at low level to avoid enemy radar.

1021
01:07:07,490 --> 01:07:10,430
最後一架飛機在23:45離開後
When the last plane leaves at 23:45,

1022
01:07:10,430 --> 01:07:14,000
跑道燈繼續保持開啟15分鐘
the runway lights stay on for 15 minutes.

1023
01:07:14,000 --> 01:07:17,570
-那是我們的突破口 -嗯
- That's our window. - Mm.

1024
01:07:17,570 --> 01:07:20,000
烏干達士兵沒有什麼威脅性
The Ugandan soldiers have nothing at stake.

1025
01:07:20,010 --> 01:07:21,800
他們一旦看到我們抵達
Once they see us when we get there,

1026
01:07:21,810 --> 01:07:23,670
-他們就會嚇得逃跑 -等一下
- they will start running. - Just a second there.

1027
01:07:23,680 --> 01:07:26,410
你說你沒有足夠的燃油 對吧?
You said you didn't have enough fuel, right?

1028
01:07:26,410 --> 01:07:28,010
這至關重要
This is crucial.

1029
01:07:28,010 --> 01:07:30,550
對 我們得在回來的路上重新加油
Yeah, we're gonna have to refuel on our way back home.

1030
01:07:30,550 --> 01:07:33,580
長官 我們可以在肯尼亞加油
Sir, Kenya will be the best place to do it.

1031
01:07:33,580 --> 01:07:34,850
莫塔
Motta.

1032
01:07:34,850 --> 01:07:37,020
這項行動不會成功的
This operation is not gonna succeed.

1033
01:07:37,020 --> 01:07:39,760
這簡直在胡鬧好嗎? 這...這簡直是在做夢
This is a charade, okay? This... it's fantasy.

1034
01:07:39,760 --> 01:07:41,760
德國人分裂了猶太人
The Germans separated the Jews.

1035
01:07:43,860 --> 01:07:46,560
做出選擇 莫塔
Selection, Motta.

1036
01:07:46,560 --> 01:07:48,830
我們不能白白坐在這兒什麼也不乾
We can't just sit here, do nothing.

1037
01:07:48,830 --> 01:07:51,030
那些是我的手下
These are my men.

1038
01:07:51,040 --> 01:07:54,500
如果他們死了就是我的責任
If they die, it's my responsibility.

1039
01:07:54,510 --> 01:07:56,940
不 莫塔 他們是以色列士兵
No, Motta. They are Israeli soldiers.

1040
01:07:56,940 --> 01:07:59,280
那是總理的責任
It's the prime minister's responsibility.

1041
01:08:03,850 --> 01:08:06,720
莫塔 你會支持我嗎?
Are you going to back me up on this, Motta?

1042
01:08:08,660 --> 01:08:09,870
第六日

1043
01:08:10,080 --> 01:08:13,000
1976年 7月2日 星期五

1044
01:08:19,000 --> 01:08:21,270
-早上好 -早上好
- Good morning. - Good morning.

1045
01:08:22,500 --> 01:08:24,100
他們在談判
They're negotiating.

1046
01:08:24,100 --> 01:08:26,070
你覺得他們會召回你嗎?
You think they're gonna call you back?

1047
01:08:26,070 --> 01:08:28,600
我不覺得這項行動會被批准 但是...
I don't think the operation's gonna be approved, but...

1048
01:08:28,610 --> 01:08:30,540
我們得訓練
we have to practice.

1049
01:08:31,640 --> 01:08:33,640
為什麼非得是你?
Why does it have to be you?

1050
01:08:33,650 --> 01:08:35,880
我們就此談過多少次了?
How many times are we gonna talk about this?

1051
01:08:35,880 --> 01:08:38,350
我們不能一直處於戰爭狀態
We can't just be at war all the time.

1052
01:08:38,350 --> 01:08:41,120
你沒有一直處於戰爭狀態 你是一個舞者
You're not at war all the time. You're a dancer.

1053
01:08:41,120 --> 01:08:43,890
我戰鬥所以你能跳舞
I fight so you can dance.

1054
01:08:46,060 --> 01:08:49,430
如果我不跳舞了呢?
What if I stop dancing?

1055
01:09:02,540 --> 01:09:03,980
喂
Yeah.

1056
01:09:06,940 --> 01:09:08,140
冷靜
Calm down.

1057
01:09:08,150 --> 01:09:09,680
安靜 安靜
Quiet, quiet.

1058
01:09:09,680 --> 01:09:11,410
聽著
Listen.

1059
01:09:11,420 --> 01:09:14,920
以色列政府已經同意談判了
The Israeli government has agreed to negotiate.

1060
01:09:14,920 --> 01:09:18,990
截止日期已經延長至週日上午11:00
The deadline has been extended until 11:00 a.m. on Sunday.

1061
01:09:20,560 --> 01:09:22,520
為表好意
As a gesture of goodwill,

1062
01:09:22,530 --> 01:09:24,630
我們已經釋放了所有的法國公民
we have released all French nationals.

1063
01:09:24,630 --> 01:09:26,560
接著一旦我們的同志被釋放
And then, once our comrades are freed,

1064
01:09:26,560 --> 01:09:28,600
你們都會重獲自由
you will all be free.

1065
01:09:28,600 --> 01:09:30,600
你們現在可以回到大房間了
You can go back to the big room now.

1066
01:09:30,600 --> 01:09:33,100
快點
Come on.

1067
01:09:34,410 --> 01:09:36,040
快點
Come on.

1068
01:09:36,040 --> 01:09:38,040
以色列從來不會談判
Israel never negotiates.

1069
01:09:38,040 --> 01:09:40,010
-大家快點 -不
- Come on, everyone. - No.

1070
01:09:41,220 --> 01:09:42,760
我們不能走

1071
01:09:43,390 --> 01:09:44,690
這是道德準則

1072
01:09:46,720 --> 01:09:48,720
和乘客待在一起是我們的職責

1073
01:09:49,520 --> 01:09:51,730
直到最後一刻

1074
01:09:55,650 --> 01:09:57,410
我明白這不容易

1075
01:10:14,650 --> 01:10:17,580
你以為你要去哪裡?
Where do you think you are going?

1076
01:10:17,580 --> 01:10:19,790
這是寫給我妻子的信
This is a letter for my wife.

1077
01:10:27,460 --> 01:10:28,890
快點
Hurry up.

1078
01:10:34,360 --> 01:10:37,140
能把這封信帶給我妻子嗎

1079
01:10:35,600 --> 01:10:37,540
-好的 先生 -謝謝
- Oui, monsieur. - Merci.

1080
01:11:20,550 --> 01:11:21,940
給你
Here.

1081
01:11:21,950 --> 01:11:24,050
我來照顧他
I'll take care of it.

1082
01:11:42,830 --> 01:11:44,090
快結束了

1083
01:11:44,600 --> 01:11:46,100
當然
Yeah.

1084
01:12:05,020 --> 01:12:06,220
這是誰?
What is this?

1085
01:12:06,220 --> 01:12:08,590
嗯? 應該來個黑人
Huh? It's supposed to be black.

1086
01:12:08,590 --> 01:12:10,660
- 嘿 他們膚色只會是黑色 – 當然
- Hey, it's the only color they had. - Yeah.

1087
01:12:16,770 --> 01:12:18,630
你在開玩笑是嗎?
You gotta be kidding me, right?

1088
01:12:18,640 --> 01:12:21,070
我要這裡最好的射擊手
I want the best shooters of the unit

1089
01:12:21,070 --> 01:12:23,070
和我一起坐梅賽德斯執行任務
inside the Mercedes with me.

1090
01:12:23,070 --> 01:12:24,970
我們將分成五組突擊航站樓
We're gonna raid the terminal in five teams.

1091
01:12:24,980 --> 01:12:26,980
約書亞領導第一組
Joshua will lead the first team.

1092
01:12:26,980 --> 01:12:28,310
穆基領導第二組
Muki, second team.

1093
01:12:28,310 --> 01:12:30,650
齊夫領導第三組
Zeev, third team.

1094
01:12:30,650 --> 01:12:33,350
阿莫斯和埃雷茲分別領導第四組和第五組
Amos and Erez, fourth and fifth.

1095
01:12:33,350 --> 01:12:36,180
我們在新航站樓跑道上登陸
We're gonna land here in the new terminal runway,

1096
01:12:36,190 --> 01:12:38,050
一直到這裡
all the way to here.

1097
01:12:38,060 --> 01:12:40,620
分坐一輛梅賽德斯和兩輛路虎出發
We're gonna go out in one Mercedes and two Land Rovers.

1098
01:12:40,620 --> 01:12:42,760
開向舊航站樓
We're gonna drive all the way to the old terminal.

1099
01:12:42,760 --> 01:12:44,330
停在塔下
We're gonna park under the tower,

1100
01:12:44,330 --> 01:12:46,800
躲避狙擊手
hidden from sniper fire.

1101
01:12:46,800 --> 01:12:48,300
兵貴神速
Surprise and speed is the key.

1102
01:12:48,300 --> 01:12:52,230
總理同意這項任務之後
And if the prime minister approves this mission,

1103
01:12:52,240 --> 01:12:53,970
我們就出發
we will go.

1104
01:12:53,970 --> 01:12:55,370
恐怖分子只需要
The terrorists only need

1105
01:12:55,370 --> 01:12:57,010
幾分鐘就能殺光所有人
a few minutes to kill everyone.

1106
01:12:57,010 --> 01:12:59,310
如果第一架飛機被偵測到並受到攻擊
What if the first plane is identified and attacked

1107
01:12:59,310 --> 01:13:02,750
在沒有支援的情況下怎麼處理?
before the rest of the force has time to land and deploy?

1108
01:13:02,750 --> 01:13:05,150
他們就沒有機會了
They won't stand a chance.

1109
01:13:05,150 --> 01:13:07,380
如果這失敗了
And if it fails,

1110
01:13:07,390 --> 01:13:10,890
對以色列國防軍的打擊 對以色列的打擊 將
the blow to the IDF, to Israel, will be...

1111
01:13:10,890 --> 01:13:12,660
是個災難
catastrophic.

1112
01:13:14,230 --> 01:13:16,790
無論如何 我的決定受內閣決定
Anyway, I am bound by the Cabinet's decision.

1113
01:13:16,790 --> 01:13:20,100
伊扎克 你就是內閣
Yitzhak, you are the Cabinet.

1114
01:13:24,200 --> 01:13:25,840
演習一次
Rehearse it.

1115
01:13:26,940 --> 01:13:28,210
他們已經在演習了
They already are.

1116
01:15:31,830 --> 01:15:35,070
全都回到原先位置
Everybody back to first position!

1117
01:15:38,500 --> 01:15:39,930
我沒有看到信號
I didn't see the signal.

1118
01:15:39,940 --> 01:15:41,040
給我擴音器
Give me the megaphone.

1119
01:15:41,040 --> 01:15:42,140
你第一個上
You're staying first.

1120
01:15:42,140 --> 01:15:43,470
你第二個上
You go second.

1121
01:15:43,470 --> 01:15:45,470
你在猶豫 又在猶豫
You're hesitating... again.

1122
01:15:45,480 --> 01:15:47,140
你斷後
You go last.

1123
01:16:01,120 --> 01:16:02,320
莫塔
Motta.

1124
01:16:04,190 --> 01:16:06,260
我要把這個行動
I'm going to recommend the operation

1125
01:16:06,260 --> 01:16:09,130
上報給拉賓和內閣 如果他說這樣可行的話
to Rabin and the Cabinet if he says it's okay.

1126
01:16:09,130 --> 01:16:10,970
你能成功嗎 約尼?
Can you do it, Yoni?

1127
01:16:15,070 --> 01:16:16,830
第七日

1128
01:16:17,040 --> 01:16:21,070
1976年 7月3日 星期六

1129
01:16:18,510 --> 01:16:20,140
有什麼會
Is there anything

1130
01:16:20,140 --> 01:16:21,480
妨礙到他們解救人質嗎?
blocking their path to the hostages?

1131
01:16:21,480 --> 01:16:23,050
沒有 長官
No, sir.

1132
01:16:23,050 --> 01:16:27,180
在航空站不會有任何問題
There are no obstacles around the terminal.

1133
01:16:27,190 --> 01:16:30,250
什麼都阻擋不了我們解救人質
Nothing to stop our men reaching the hostages.

1134
01:16:30,250 --> 01:16:32,920
在他們離開之前 我想合張影
I want the photograph to reach the men before they leave.

1135
01:16:32,920 --> 01:16:34,460
謝謝
Thank you.

1136
01:16:37,430 --> 01:16:40,330
沒有什麼能阻礙這次的行動
There's nothing to stop the operation from proceeding.

1137
01:16:40,330 --> 01:16:42,360
所以現在你必須做個選擇
So now you have to make a decision.

1138
01:16:42,370 --> 01:16:44,000
如果我還是上將的話
If I was still a general,

1139
01:16:44,000 --> 01:16:46,070
我不會同意這次任務
I would never approve this mission.

1140
01:16:46,070 --> 01:16:48,570
這有極大的危險
It's a huge risk.

1141
01:16:48,570 --> 01:16:52,340
你們知道的 這件事有非常多的變數
There will be casualties. You all know that.

1142
01:16:52,340 --> 01:16:56,340
關於這次的任務不能有任何的猶疑
What we cannot doubt is the mission.

1143
01:16:56,350 --> 01:16:58,310
我們必須完成這次任務
We must complete our objective.

1144
01:16:58,320 --> 01:17:01,120
我們一定要在三分鐘內到達航空站
We need to get to the terminal in three minutes,

1145
01:17:01,120 --> 01:17:03,890
把所有恐怖分子解決並解救人質
kill all the terrorists and rescue the hostages.

1146
01:17:03,890 --> 01:17:05,450
不能被其他事情阻礙
And we don't stop for nothing

1147
01:17:05,460 --> 01:17:07,890
直到所有人質安全
until all the hostages are safe.

1148
01:17:07,890 --> 01:17:10,630
我們將起飛到達火力範圍
We will take off and get into striking range

1149
01:17:10,630 --> 01:17:12,560
在等待內閣的決定時
while we wait for the Cabinet's decision.

1150
01:17:12,560 --> 01:17:13,930
出發
Let's go.

1151
01:17:13,930 --> 01:17:15,270
所有人上飛機
Everybody on board.

1152
01:17:51,670 --> 01:17:53,510
波尼
Boni.

1153
01:19:30,700 --> 01:19:32,570
- 總理 - 莫塔
- Prime Minister. - Motta.

1154
01:19:32,570 --> 01:19:34,600
總理
Prime Minister.

1155
01:19:34,610 --> 01:19:38,170
我的職位在座各位應該都知道
My position is well known to those in this room.

1156
01:19:38,180 --> 01:19:40,740
我肯定內閣會支持你的決定
I am sure that the Cabinet will support your decision

1157
01:19:40,740 --> 01:19:42,680
承擔集體的責任
and take collective responsib...

1158
01:19:42,680 --> 01:19:46,010
西蒙 飛機已經起飛了
Shimon, the plane's already left.

1159
01:19:46,020 --> 01:19:47,680
我們可以調他們回來 如果內閣決定
We'll call them back if the Cabinet decides

1160
01:19:47,690 --> 01:19:49,280
不執行任務
not to proceed with the operation.

1161
01:19:49,290 --> 01:19:50,620
莫塔
Motta.

1162
01:19:50,620 --> 01:19:53,790
你把這次行動報告給內閣了嗎?
Do you recommend this operation to the Cabinet?

1163
01:19:53,790 --> 01:19:55,490
是的 總理
Yes, Prime Minister.

1164
01:19:55,490 --> 01:19:57,760
先生們 阿莫斯將進行一個陳述
Gentlemen, Amos will now read a statement,

1165
01:19:57,760 --> 01:19:59,390
之後我們進行投票
and then we will vote.

1166
01:19:59,400 --> 01:20:01,530
政府部門決定
"The government resolves to approve

1167
01:20:01,530 --> 01:20:03,060
贊同實施營救任務
"implementation of a rescue operation

1168
01:20:03,070 --> 01:20:05,100
由以色列國防軍實施
"by the Israeli Defense Forces

1169
01:20:05,100 --> 01:20:07,440
解救恩德培的人質
"to free the hostages at Entebbe, according to

1170
01:20:07,440 --> 01:20:09,170
依照國防部門
"the plan submitted by the defense minister

1171
01:20:09,170 --> 01:20:11,370
和參謀長提供的營救計劃實施
and the chief of staff."

1172
01:20:11,370 --> 01:20:13,140
在座各位是否支持?
All those in favor?

1173
01:20:19,380 --> 01:20:21,750
那就這樣行動
So be it.

1174
01:20:21,750 --> 01:20:25,160
雷霆行動按計劃執行
Operation Thunderbolt will proceed as planned.

1175
01:20:42,610 --> 01:20:44,770
特拉維夫指揮中心
Tel Aviv Command Center,

1176
01:20:44,770 --> 01:20:46,610
雷霆行動開始
Thunderbolt is a go.

1177
01:20:46,610 --> 01:20:49,780
重覆 雷霆行動開始
I repeat, Thunderbolt is a go.

1178
01:20:51,220 --> 01:20:53,550
預計到達恩德培時間為
ETA, Entebbe...

1179
01:20:53,550 --> 01:20:55,320
23:45.
23:45

1180
01:20:55,320 --> 01:20:57,360
減四小時 32
Minus four hours, 32.

1181
01:21:04,530 --> 01:21:06,390
那是我們的通道
That's our door.

1182
01:21:06,400 --> 01:21:09,700
是控制塔的第四層
It's the fourth from the control tower.

1183
01:22:20,740 --> 01:22:22,740
胡安·帕布洛
Juan Pablo...

1184
01:22:26,580 --> 01:22:29,110
我真希望和你待在家
I wish I was at home with you.

1185
01:22:30,610 --> 01:22:32,780
我真希望我在家
I wish I was at home.

1186
01:22:34,620 --> 01:22:37,260
我不知道我的家在哪裡
I don't know where my home is.

1187
01:22:39,520 --> 01:22:42,630
當這些過去之後我們需要一個家
Think we need to find a home when this is over.

1188
01:22:44,760 --> 01:22:46,500
在某個地方
Somewhere.

1189
01:22:48,300 --> 01:22:50,440
和平的地方
Somewhere peaceful.

1190
01:23:03,350 --> 01:23:05,850
賈貝爾認為以色列軍會來
Jaber thinks the Israelis will come

1191
01:23:05,850 --> 01:23:07,520
並且會殺了我們
and they'll kill us.

1192
01:23:09,790 --> 01:23:13,560
如果這真的發生 我們必須說出我們的想法
And then if that happens, we have to make a statement.

1193
01:23:14,960 --> 01:23:17,530
這是我們在這裡的原因
And that's why we are here.

1194
01:23:22,270 --> 01:23:24,670
我在擔心博斯
I'm worried about Bose.

1195
01:23:26,500 --> 01:23:28,370
他在害怕
He's scared.

1196
01:23:29,940 --> 01:23:32,340
你知道的 他很脆弱
He is weak. You know that.

1197
01:23:33,940 --> 01:23:36,480
他們都很害怕
They're all scared.

1198
01:23:36,480 --> 01:23:38,420
賈貝爾也是
Even Jaber.

1199
01:23:41,280 --> 01:23:43,450
我不害怕
I'm not scared.

1200
01:23:45,760 --> 01:23:47,530
我看清了
I see it.

1201
01:23:50,960 --> 01:23:53,200
現在我看清了所有事情
I see everything now.

1202
01:23:55,530 --> 01:23:57,800
我想你可能是對的
I think maybe you were right.

1203
01:24:00,840 --> 01:24:04,640
但是如果我沒有來這裡
But if I never came here,

1204
01:24:04,640 --> 01:24:06,580
那又意味著什麼?
what would that mean?

1205
01:24:09,910 --> 01:24:12,320
不 你幫不上忙
No, there's nothing you can do.

1206
01:24:13,950 --> 01:24:16,320
任何人都幫不上忙
There's nothing anyone can do.

1207
01:24:19,360 --> 01:24:21,230
沒有人能逃出去
There's no escape.

1208
01:24:22,990 --> 01:24:24,730
沒有人
No escape.

1209
01:24:31,640 --> 01:24:34,610
或許我就不應該來
I think maybe I shouldn't have come.

1210
01:24:38,010 --> 01:24:41,380
- 或許我就不應該來 – 女士
- I think maybe I shouldn't have come... - Miss.

1211
01:24:41,380 --> 01:24:43,550
這些電話都沒用了
Those phones are not working.

1212
01:24:43,550 --> 01:24:46,020
那裡還有電話
There are other telephones over there.

1213
01:25:02,000 --> 01:25:04,300
再見 胡安·帕布洛
Good-bye, Juan Pablo.

1214
01:25:30,130 --> 01:25:33,630
如果任務失敗 把這個遞交上去
If the mission fails, submit it.

1215
01:25:39,140 --> 01:25:41,570
您認為的任務失敗是什麼呢 總理?
And what's your definition of failure, Prime Minister?

1216
01:25:43,440 --> 01:25:47,780
25位人質在馬洛特死亡 這是個災難
25 hostages died at Ma'alot, and it was a disaster.

1217
01:25:47,780 --> 01:25:52,380
這一次 營救25人左右就是成功
This time around, 25 or less will be a success.

1218
01:26:03,990 --> 01:26:05,700
你早該走了

1219
01:26:05,820 --> 01:26:06,870
走？

1220
01:26:07,710 --> 01:26:08,870
去哪

1221
01:26:09,070 --> 01:26:10,620
去叢林嗎

1222
01:26:13,500 --> 01:26:15,290
不 我在想胡安·帕布洛

1223
01:26:17,290 --> 01:26:19,380
他不適合這次行動

1224
01:26:21,380 --> 01:26:23,510
需要我們最優秀的兩個人

1225
01:26:28,690 --> 01:26:30,260
對不起

1226
01:26:32,520 --> 01:26:33,980
胡安·帕布洛是對的

1227
01:26:37,520 --> 01:26:39,150
我想來這

1228
01:26:41,820 --> 01:26:43,510
我想來

1229
01:27:17,100 --> 01:27:19,030
現在情況怎麼樣?
What's the status?

1230
01:27:19,040 --> 01:27:20,970
最後一架民用飛機剛起飛
Last civilian flight just took off.

1231
01:27:20,970 --> 01:27:23,800
應該在十分鐘內著陸
Should be landing in ten minutes.

1232
01:27:23,810 --> 01:27:25,840
用無線電通信情況怎麼樣?
How about the radio communication?

1233
01:27:25,840 --> 01:27:30,010
有許多干擾 但是能夠聯繫上
There's lots of static, but they're getting through.

1234
01:27:30,010 --> 01:27:32,750
因此 目前來說 還不錯
So... so far, so good.

1235
01:27:32,750 --> 01:27:34,750
好的 先生們
Okay, gentlemen.

1236
01:27:34,750 --> 01:27:36,080
情況就是這樣
This is it.

1237
01:28:00,510 --> 01:28:01,910
到了
Okay.

1238
01:28:18,100 --> 01:28:19,660
我們突擊航站樓時
As soon as we hit the terminal,

1239
01:28:19,660 --> 01:28:21,160
你們開始射擊控制塔
you start shooting the control tower.

1240
01:28:21,160 --> 01:28:22,800
- 好  – 你明白了嗎?
- Okay. Yeah. - Yes?

1241
01:28:22,800 --> 01:28:25,540
兵貴神速
Surprise and speed is the key.

1242
01:29:21,220 --> 01:29:22,920
出發
Here we go.

1243
01:31:16,840 --> 01:31:18,110
他們開槍了
They are reporting gunfire.

1244
01:31:19,240 --> 01:31:20,910
現在太早了不能開槍
It's too early for gunfire.

1245
01:31:20,910 --> 01:31:22,240
停下
Stop.

1246
01:31:24,110 --> 01:31:25,880
是阿明嗎?
Is that Amin?

1247
01:31:27,320 --> 01:31:28,280
無論發生什麼
Whatever happens...

1248
01:31:29,490 --> 01:31:31,320
我們做的是對的事情
...we did the right thing.

1249
01:31:33,920 --> 01:31:36,060
- 是以色列兵 – 關上門
- It's the Israelis. - Cover the door.

1250
01:31:36,060 --> 01:31:37,360
關上門!
Cover the doors!

1251
01:31:37,360 --> 01:31:39,060
行動!
Go, go, go!

1252
01:31:40,450 --> 01:31:41,570
我們得殺了他們

1253
01:31:45,300 --> 01:31:46,750
我來

1254
01:32:08,490 --> 01:32:10,760
趴下
Get down.

1255
01:32:10,760 --> 01:32:12,260
所有人趴下!
Everybody, get down!

1256
01:32:58,070 --> 01:32:59,140
穆基 走
Muki, go.

1257
01:32:59,140 --> 01:33:01,140
走
Go.

1258
01:33:20,400 --> 01:33:21,600
大衛 進門!
David, take the door!

1259
01:34:27,560 --> 01:34:30,060
- 以色列兵 所有人趴下 – 前進
- IDF! Everybody down! - Move forward!

1260
01:34:30,070 --> 01:34:32,670
前進!前進!
Move forward! Move forward!

1261
01:34:32,670 --> 01:34:34,400
所有人趴下!
Everybody down!

1262
01:34:34,400 --> 01:34:37,240
- 前進!前進! – 停!停止射擊
- Move forward! Move forward! - Stop! Don't shoot!

1263
01:34:37,240 --> 01:34:38,670
- 停 – 人質在這裡 人質
- Stop! - Hostage! Hostage!

1264
01:34:38,680 --> 01:34:39,610
手榴彈!
Grenade!

1265
01:36:40,200 --> 01:36:42,100
我們在飛機上
We are in the air.

1266
01:36:42,100 --> 01:36:44,600
我們安全營救了102位人質
We have 102 hostages safe on board.

1267
01:36:44,600 --> 01:36:48,770
重覆 我們安全營救了102位人質
I repeat, we have 102 hostages safe on board.

1268
01:37:00,120 --> 01:37:03,590
總理 祝賀你 你成功了
Congratulations on your success, Prime Minister.

1269
01:37:12,100 --> 01:37:15,100
我們拯救了一百多人的生命
We saved a hundred lives.

1270
01:37:15,100 --> 01:37:17,760
我們應當為此感到自豪
And we should be proud of that.

1271
01:37:17,770 --> 01:37:20,130
西蒙,但是如果我們沒有協商成功的話
But if we cannot negotiate, Shimon,

1272
01:37:20,140 --> 01:37:22,140
這場戰爭將永不會停止
this war will never end.

1273
01:38:04,750 --> 01:38:08,290
因為劫機去世的四位人質：
讓-雅克·米默尼 艾達·布洛維茨 帕斯科·科恩 朵拉·布洛赫

1274
01:38:08,710 --> 01:38:13,630
45名烏干達士兵 5名巴基斯坦人 2名德國人 也在恩德培行動中去世

1275
01:38:20,210 --> 01:38:27,400
1995年 總理伊扎克·拉賓在簽署了以色列與巴勒斯坦的和平協議後被一名猶太極端分子刺殺

1276
01:38:31,730 --> 01:38:38,820
西蒙·佩雷斯在之後開始支持與巴勒斯坦和平談判
他於2016年因高齡去世

1277
01:38:49,850 --> 01:39:00,390
約拿森·內塔尼亞胡上校是唯一戰死的以色列士兵
他的弟弟在他死後踏入政壇
併在1996年當上總理

1278
01:39:03,020 --> 01:39:08,940
在今日 以巴兩國再無和平談判
2018年3月


